text: Tham Kook Chin (born 7 November 1943) is a Malaysian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle lightweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Malaysia Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
